name: //\\The Corruption of OG Astro//\\
description:
"Many months deep in the
metaverse has started to warp
reality for OG_Astro. A thick
shiny lustre has formed over the
pixels. Lights crackle and fizz as
they burn through into the skin -
All things in time will be
devoured." This is the first
piece in a series exploring the
dynamic interaction between art
and the new digital territories.
